<div class='col-lg-7 col-lg-offset-1'>
<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='880' id='t-880'>So, this is a story</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='2904' id='t-2904'>about how we know what we know.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:16
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5690' id='t-5690'>It's a story about this woman,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='8611' id='t-8611'>Natalia Rybczynski.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='10912' id='t-10912'>She's a paleobiologist,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12984' id='t-12984'>which means she specializes
in digging up really old dead stuff.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='16837' id='t-16837'>(Audio) Natalia Rybczynski: Yeah,
I had someone call me &quot;Dr. Dead Things.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='20363' id='t-20363'>Latif Nasser: And I think
she's particularly interesting</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23016' id='t-23016'>because of where she digs that stuff up,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='24954' id='t-24954'>way above the Arctic Circle
in the remote Canadian tundra.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='29901' id='t-29901'>Now, one summer day in 2006,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='32980' id='t-32980'>she was at a dig site called
the Fyles Leaf Bed,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='36195' id='t-36195'>which is less than 10 degrees latitude
away from the magnetic north pole.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='40797' id='t-40797'>(Audio) NR: Really, it's not
going to sound very exciting,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='43548' id='t-43548'>because it was a day of walking
with your backpack and your GPS</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='47602' id='t-47602'>and notebook and just picking up
anything that might be a fossil.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='51704' id='t-51704'>LN: And at some point,
she noticed something.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='54403' id='t-54403'>(Audio) NR: Rusty, kind of rust-colored,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='56594' id='t-56594'>about the size of the palm of my hand.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58553' id='t-58553'>It was just lying on the surface.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='60871' id='t-60871'>LN: And at first she thought
it was just a splinter of wood,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='64347' id='t-64347'>because that's the sort of thing
people had found</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66664' id='t-66664'>at the Fyles Leaf Bed before --
prehistoric plant parts.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='70107' id='t-70107'>But that night, back at camp ...</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='72940' id='t-72940'>(Audio) NR: ... I get out the hand lens,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='74893' id='t-74893'>I'm looking a little bit
more closely and realizing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='77314' id='t-77314'>it doesn't quite look
like this has tree rings.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='79742' id='t-79742'>Maybe it's a preservation thing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='81330' id='t-81330'>but it looks really like ...</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='83628' id='t-83628'>bone.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='84853' id='t-84853'>LN: Huh. So over the next four years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='87766' id='t-87766'>she went to that spot over and over,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='90724' id='t-90724'>and eventually collected 30 fragments
of that exact same bone,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96284' id='t-96284'>most of them really tiny.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='98522' id='t-98522'>(Audio) NR: It's not a whole lot.
It fits in a small Ziploc bag.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='102982' id='t-102982'>LN: And she tried to piece them
together like a jigsaw puzzle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='106941' id='t-106941'>But it was challenging.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='108410' id='t-108410'>(Audio) NR: It's broken up
into so many little tiny pieces,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='111254' id='t-111254'>I'm trying to use sand and putty,
and it's not looking good.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='115536' id='t-115536'>So finally, we used a 3D surface scanner.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='120727' id='t-120727'>LN: Ooh!
NR: Yeah, right?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='122340' id='t-122340'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123804' id='t-123804'>LN: It turns out it was way easier
to do it virtually.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='126571' id='t-126571'>(Audio) NR: It's kind of magical
when it all fits together.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='129365' id='t-129365'>LN: How certain were you
that you had it right,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='131588' id='t-131588'>that you had put it together
in the right way?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='133757' id='t-133757'>Was there a potential that you'd
put it together a different way</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='136795' id='t-136795'>and have, like, a parakeet or something?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='138761' id='t-138761'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='140150' id='t-140150'>(Audio) NR: (Laughs) Um, no.
No, we got this.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144242' id='t-144242'>LN: What she had, she discovered,
was a tibia, a leg bone,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='148107' id='t-148107'>and specifically, one that belonged
to a cloven-hoofed mammal,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='152131' id='t-152131'>so something like a cow or a sheep.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='155004' id='t-155004'>But it couldn't have been either of those.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='157488' id='t-157488'>It was just too big.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='159822' id='t-159822'>(Audio) NR: The size of this thing,
it was huge. It's a really big animal.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='163910' id='t-163910'>LN: So what animal could it be?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='167291' id='t-167291'>Having hit a wall, she showed
one of the fragments</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='169895' id='t-169895'>to some colleagues of hers in Colorado,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='172491' id='t-172491'>and they had an idea.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='174244' id='t-174244'>(Audio) NR: We took a saw,
and we nicked just the edge of it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='179315' id='t-179315'>and there was this really interesting
smell that comes from it.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='186521' id='t-186521'>LN: It smelled kind of like singed flesh.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='189308' id='t-189308'>It was a smell that Natalia recognized</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='191965' id='t-191965'>from cutting up skulls
in her gross anatomy lab:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='195932' id='t-195932'>collagen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='197120' id='t-197120'>Collagen is what gives
structure to our bones.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='199801' id='t-199801'>And usually, after so many years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201983' id='t-201983'>it breaks down.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203158' id='t-203158'>But in this case, the Arctic had acted
like a natural freezer and preserved it.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='208190' id='t-208190'>Then a year or two later,
Natalia was at a conference in Bristol,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='211837' id='t-211837'>and she saw that a colleague
of hers named Mike Buckley</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='215055' id='t-215055'>was demoing this new process
that he called &quot;collagen fingerprinting.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='221284' id='t-221284'>It turns out that different species
have slightly different structures</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='224951' id='t-224951'>of collagen,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226127' id='t-226127'>so if you get a collagen profile
of an unknown bone,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='228967' id='t-228967'>you can compare it
to those of known species,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231185' id='t-231185'>and, who knows, maybe you get a match.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='234546' id='t-234546'>So she shipped him one of the fragments,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='237849' id='t-237849'>FedEx.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='239167' id='t-239167'>(Audio) NR: Yeah, you want to track it.
It's kind of important.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243001' id='t-243001'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:15
</data>
